M||tx|---
M||titl|Split Combined Hook Computations
M||impa|md
M||impa|avoids recomputing independent steps
M||tags|rerender, useMemo, useEffect, dependencies, op
M||tx|---
M|Spli|tx|When a hook contains multiple independent tasks w/ different dependencies, split them into separate hooks. A combined hook reruns all tasks when any dependency changes, even if some tasks don't use the changed value.
M|Spli|**In|**
M|Spli|tx|```tsx
M|Spli|tx|const sortedProducts = useMemo(() => {
M|Spli|tx|const filtered = pd.filter((p) => p.category === category)
M|Spli|tx|const sorted = filtered.toSorted((a, b) =>
M|Spli|sort|b.price - a.price
M|Spli|tx|)
M|Spli|tx|return sorted
M|Spli|tx|}, [pd, category, sortOrder])
M|Spli|tx|```
M|Spli|**Co|**
M|Spli|tx|```tsx
M|Spli|tx|const filteredProducts = useMemo(
M|Spli|tx|() => pd.filter((p) => p.category === category),
M|Spli|tx|[pd, category]
M|Spli|tx|)
M|Spli|tx|const sortedProducts = useMemo(
M|Spli|tx|() =>
M|Spli|tx|filteredProducts.toSorted((a, b) =>
M|Spli|sort|b.price - a.price
M|Spli|tx|),
M|Spli|tx|[filteredProducts, sortOrder]
M|Spli|tx|)
M|Spli|tx|```
M|Spli|This|
M|Spli|**In|**
M|Spli|tx|```tsx
M|Spli|tx|useEffect(() => {
M|Spli|tx|an.trackPageView(pathname)
M|Spli|tx|document.title = `${pageTitle} \| My App`
M|Spli|tx|}, [pathname, pageTitle])
M|Spli|tx|```
M|Spli|**Co|**
M|Spli|tx|```tsx
M|Spli|tx|useEffect(() => {
M|Spli|tx|an.trackPageView(pathname)
M|Spli|tx|}, [pathname])
M|Spli|tx|useEffect(() => {
M|Spli|tx|document.title = `${pageTitle} \| My App`
M|Spli|tx|}, [pageTitle])
M|Spli|tx|```
M|Spli|**No|** If your project has [rc Compiler](https://rc.dv/learn/rc-compiler) enabled, it automatically optimizes dependency tracking and may handle some of these cases for you.